{"hbad1f1f2g1f25g4ea3gbe32g62163efeb065": ["Something the matter? Besides the obvious, that is.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "18a030f1-ea8d-4088-b3c1-e650c0b78a1d"], "h49ef0b56g2369g46c8gabf8g345e795dd9a6": ["My name is [GEN_PlayerName2_85df4a15-4d9b-4f68-0512-d104305d8dac], by the way.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "942ed032-a492-7a18-1931-a14612e2bc35"], "h6ffa4d51g6024g451ag9ceegd9c8406b1323": ["You can call me Shadowheart.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "cd413dc8-d7d7-ec87-fb54-0352b174ee66"], "h447f0478g7b45g4192g89cfg7f20c75ccfdc": ["I'm Shadowheart. Enchanted to meet you - as much as circumstances allow.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "cd413dc8-d7d7-ec87-fb54-0352b174ee66"], "h9bdf2adcg5f5bg46cegb015gf01b63ac369d": ["'Shadowheart'? Unusual name.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "7b95f4a8-0555-13a6-e750-e1d71692a384"], "h45c9a6e0g0bfag41b2g8463g6f7e2172f586": ["Pondering my name won't get us off this ship. Let's stow the small talk until we're safe, shall we?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "2baa0a29-2b7c-e631-b0f0-914a5a6d111f"], "h04611ff2g9ff7g4286gb10ag7b2c172dfc86": ["Any suggestions for how to proceed?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "bc170739-387a-9d3a-67a2-2ba49a766094"], "h1644fd16gb248g4ce3gafdegb740909bfbef": ["Well, jumping overboard is hardly an option - so that leaves us with taking control of this ship.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "c9c7e4e2-51f7-96df-4683-d35df3cd4605"], "h26952522g158dg42adga511ga58e33044838": ["Provided we can figure out how to do that, of course...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "03317891-27db-863a-229f-d56ef48db675"], "h4c9ed37cg9225g4db2g930fga229013d9438": ["Let's keep going.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "6796ed99-f309-0514-04c8-64bd62b301f7"], "hcd10841bgdbbfg4a0bg8192ge81d856dd9f2": ["I'm right behind you.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "c020e1c8-e0e2-63ae-9a87-07c6e8c37a8e"], "h49690d3bgf514g44efg8bceg6d53b4341893": ["Never mind. Let's keep going.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "7d55ec28-ae1d-23c5-cdc6-1a110cb5ddfd"], "hc4220b61g3574g4709ga409gfe414b42c8a5": ["You're keen to chat, for someone in mortal peril. What's the matter?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_ShadowheartFollower.html", "eb3fb344-015f-19e6-d338-ca5cd6551ec9"]}